ITermTransformer
public class NormalizeArrayTermsTransformer
extends AbstractTermTransformer

Created by christopher on 08/01/14.

Normalizes Array accessors by turning them into more "natural" representations such as "arr[0]" instead of, for example, int::select(heap,array,arr(Z(0(#)).
